node.text: The 2005 Shelby GR-1 was originally a concept. But apparently @superformancellc will be building these. The original concept had an all aluminum 6.4L V10, instead it will be produced with a supercharged V8 still good for 750 hp along with a dual clutch 6 speed.  There will be 200 examples made in either polished aluminum or painted. Prices will start at $250k. Yall dig it or nah? #shelby #gr1 #concept
